https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mLPZMskrvJggwxO4kbnBWvzzjjw.jpg AAA BUZZ COMMUNICATION TOUR 2011 DELUXE EDITION is the sixteenth concert DVD and nineteenth overall video released by AAA. This DVD contains the footage of a concert held at SAITAMA SUPER ARENA on June 26th 2011. First press editions comes with two postcards. The DVD charted for 10 weeks and peaked #2 on Oricon Music DVD Charts. AAA Buzz Communication Tour 2011 Deluxe Edition
